title: For Sale:  1st generation AK bayonet
location: dover, akron, massillon, Ohio, United States
postcontent: 1st generation Romanian AK 47 bayonet.  Brown synthetic handle, approximately 5 3/4" sawback blade.  Metal scabbard with lug to fit into bayonet blade to make wire cutters.  Great piece of history and a must for your collection.
